 No. | Dependency | Computation method | Result
 ----+------------+--------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1.  |            | given              | sk = 78ea7f9a176eec0bf7f4fb4ef1020ae3b8ebd9fa80c1337c70e0ec911f6cca31
 2.  |            | given              | timestamp = 1772036778848
 3.  |            | lastNonce          | nonce = 9223372036854775807
 4.  | 1,         | secp256k1          | pk = 0485e31ef85dca84b1b6134b6cef9e70f43c34586404c74fac172972aae18d1d4a45e5b116334796deb6e210e1a8c5962b9f30edcd5b723200234725c83eae56f6
 5.  | 2, 4, 3,   | registry           | value = (1772036778848, 0485e31ef85dca84b1b6134b6cef9e70f43c34586404c74fac172972aae18d1d4a45e5b116334796deb6e210e1a8c5962b9f30edcd5b723200234725c83eae56f6, 9223372036854775807)
 6.  | 5,         | protobuf           | toSign = 2a65aa01620a092a0710c0adfbd992670a462a44ca01410485e31ef85dca84b1b6134b6cef9e70f43c34586404c74fac172972aae18d1d4a45e5b116334796deb6e210e1a8c5962b9f30edcd5b723200234725c83eae56f60a0d2a0b10feffffffffffffffff01
